{"id": 3127, "genre": 1001, "title": "线上社交时，你发现自己有哪些不知不觉被绑架的时候？", "description": "网民们的新一代peer pressure。（题图来自：iStock ©️ nadia_bormotova ）", "record_count": 1904, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20200118221244YomeNGMqE3aIli7D.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2020-01-18T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 352514, "content": "很好很棒啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1533986}, {"id": 352522, "content": "嗨，在不？又不说什么事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1688322}, {"id": 352023, "content": "不喜欢用微信又不能卸", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636761}, {"id": 352026, "content": "必须是没什么大事直接打电话过来", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1637308}, {"id": 352029, "content": "安装新的app要求开通各种手机权限", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677796}, {"id": 352548, "content": "猜你喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640758}, {"id": 352299, "content": "大群里面有一个人开始夸夸 不想跟上夸 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805935}, {"id": 352302, "content": "在微信群发通知的那种，没要求收到回复的通知，总有些贱人要去回一个收到。然后二百人的群，不停的复写收到，害的手机响一百八十次", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680379}, {"id": 352560, "content": "在不在？ ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1063095}, {"id": 352562, "content": "大群里学校领导发消息，一定要列队不同回复", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1690512}, {"id": 352053, "content": "说个老套的，不转不是中国人", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1463931}, {"id": 352068, "content": "“收到請回復”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1582791}, {"id": 352344, "content": "亲戚发来不想接听的视频通话，学校要求加的微信QQ群", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1643907}, {"id": 352358, "content": "帮忙投个票噢～点进链接xxx号", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1681328}, {"id": 352362, "content": "当我面临压倒性权势个体或群体时，我自知无力强辩、无力反驳时", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1681643}, {"id": 352107, "content": "视频通话", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1644649}, {"id": 352112, "content": "未征得同意要求视频通话", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677976}, {"id": 352628, "content": "这", "image": "img/option/option/20200907162151lUNKGu1zFkrvTS0H.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297776}, {"id": 352374, "content": "当你在注册一个新用户的时候总是跑出来各种条款，为了注册成功只能选择同意，不管里面的条款有多霸道", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506438}, {"id": 352631, "content": "同寝室的室友聊天，老是背锅，说实话很恶心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1693099}, {"id": 352646, "content": "“看到请回复一下”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1519451}, {"id": 352651, "content": "拼多多砍一刀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1693708}, {"id": 352141, "content": "微信上传身份证照片，不上传不给用…\n\n转发朋友圈24小时，即可获得某某礼包…\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661803}, {"id": 352662, "content": "消息必须回复 不然就是不礼貌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1694022}, {"id": 352154, "content": "@全体成员", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578832}, {"id": 351916, "content": "除了工作，聊天从来不发表情会让人觉得很严肃或者不用心", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351917, "content": "对热搜事件不怎么感兴趣，但是别人玩梗的时候自己get不到就很难受", "image": null, "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351918, "content": "语音不得不听／转成文字", "image": null, "praise_count": 317, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351919, "content": "被别人@不回复也会显得不礼貌", "image": null, "praise_count": 230, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 352175, "content": "收到请回复", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1617082}, {"id": 351920, "content": "只要有人回复你参与过的动态什么的就会被提醒", "image": null, "praise_count": 149, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351921, "content": "面对艾特全体通知消息时，一定要礼貌回复收到，毕恭毕敬到难受。", "image": null, "praise_count": 112, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291669}, {"id": 351922, "content": "全体艾特想回就回，不想回就不回啊，没必要回复了才算看到吧？这个看自己。如果是反复的艾特，那肯定是要回复得", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1477707}, {"id": 351923, "content": "被艾特。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749248}, {"id": 351924, "content": "拼多多砍一刀", "image": null, "praise_count": 149, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921335}, {"id": 351925, "content": "雪崩的时候没有一朵雪花是无辜的？关我什么事？", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522195}, {"id": 352437, "content": "朋友说：快点赞我朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572052}, {"id": 351926, "content": "发朋友圈要部分屏蔽", "image": null, "praise_count": 186, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282904}, {"id": 352438, "content": "在么", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1684279}, {"id": 351927, "content": "在社交軟件上沒說明要找女朋友就是想約炮了🙄️", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786838}, {"id": 351928, "content": "收到请回复", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088561}, {"id": 351930, "content": "用左手刷手机在逛B站的时候经常不小心按到赞或踩\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484179}, {"id": 351931, "content": "看完别人发的消息会显示已阅", "image": null, "praise_count": 63, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1580529}, {"id": 351933, "content": "聊了半天又是色情产业加你", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948915}, {"id": 351935, "content": "别人发了有关你的动态 不评论显得不礼貌...", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1677536}, {"id": 352195, "content": "生活的仪式感 从来不止在朋友圈里", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664973}, {"id": 352453, "content": "朋友圈第一条点赞，谢谢！\n后来不看朋友圈，\n却还在使用微信。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1681443}, {"id": 352454, "content": "qq越来越像辅助工具\n从不聊天\n只用邮箱、游戏登入等", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1681443}, {"id": 352459, "content": "已经用QQ沟通日常工作了，还要被迫用私人微信在私人时间里沟通工作。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212527}, {"id": 351948, "content": "通知群，不提示怕错过了，开提示一百个收到收到", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469748}]}